<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>GetFit - Keeping Up Your Motivation</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      color: white;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .hero-container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-image: url('/erasebg-transformed (31).png'); /* Replace this */
      background-size: cover;
      background-position-y: 0%;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #1e90ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #4682b4;
    }

    .progress-container {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 5px;
      background-color: #ddd;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      height: 100%;
      width: 50%;
      background-color: #1e90ff;
      transition: width 0.25s ease;
    }

    /* Responsive Adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-container {
        background-size: contain;
        background-position: top center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        padding-top: 60px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .btn {
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 12px 24px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .btn {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Keeping up your motivation is key</h1>
      <p>Celebrate the small wins and remember why you started. It shouldnâ€™t be about a number, but rather the feeling you get when you accomplish each milestone.</p>
      <a href="/page16" class="btn">Continue</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="progress-container">
    <div class="progress-bar" id="progress-bar"></div>
  </div>

  <script>
    window.addEventListener("scroll", function () {
      const docHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
      const scrollPosition = window.scrollY;
      const scrollPercentage = (scrollPosition / docHeight) * 100;
      document.getElementById("progress-bar").style.width = scrollPercentage + "%";
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
